es are flat. Diagnose the problem and fix my recipe.\u001b[49m            \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;1m! \u001b[0mI'll help diagnose your flat pancakes! Let me break this down into       \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m  parallel tasks:                                                          \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m  1. \u001b[1mdiagnose-flat-pancakes\u001b[0m \u2014 Investigate common causes                    \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m  2. \u001b[1mfix-pancake-recipe\u001b[0m \u2014 Apply the fix (after diagnosis)                  \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m  3. \u001b[1mimprove-presentation\u001b[0m \u2014 Make them look great (parallel with fix)       \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m  4. \u001b[1mfinal-taste-test\u001b[0m \u2014 Verify the result                                  \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m  Creating the task graph now...                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u001b[38;5;8m\u2502\n\u2502\u001b[39m                                                                           \u00